description:
Time to stand up for our Country/Freedom/Human rights Australia 🇦🇺. 
look to Hong Kong at their reaction, they were out in the streets protesting for months on end! They know what it’s like to live under a communist regime. We’ve all had it too easy in this country and can’t comprehend what is happening or how bad things are going to get if we don’t all WAKE UP and STAND UP!! 
new protests are coming in early September but make it a habit of protesting in your day to day life! 
The spirit or our Anzacs is NOT dead!!! 🇦🇺⚔️
